'''Tutlayin timaziɣin tisemranin''' d yiwet n tegrawt n [[tutlayin timaziɣin]] ttmeslayen  yis [[imaziɣen]] n [[Libya]] d [[Maṣer|Miẓra]]. Deg tegrawt-a, llant wazal n 7 n [[tutlayt|tutlayin]], gar-asent snat n [[tutlayt yettwaggzen s ungar|tutlayin negren-t]] ([[Tasuknit]] d [[Tazuregt|Tzuregt]]), ma d 5 niḍen ttwaggzen-t s waṭas s umihi n ungar aladɣa [[Tawilant]].

== Tutlayin timaziɣin n usmar ==
* [[Tanfust]]: ttmeslayen-tt deg ugafa utrim n Libya d kra n yimezdaɣ deg unẓul n [[Tunes]].
* [[Tasiwit]]: ttmeslayen-tt imaziɣen n [[Siwa]] i d-yezgan deg utaram afellay n [[Maṣer|Miẓra]].
* [[Tawilant]]: ttmeslayen-tt imezdaɣ n temdint n [[Ujila]] i d-yezgan deg usamar n [[Libya]], tutlayt-a tettwaggez s waṭas s umihi n wengar.
* [[Tasuknit]]: llan ttmeslayen yis imezdaɣ n [[Fezzan]] maca tura tenger.

